This project goal to implementation two Perl.
    1. Create application /home/gen_csv/gen_csv.pl:
        - CSV File Path: /home/csv_folder/
        - First column record timer, format: yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss 
        - It can Receive 2 parameter and write it to the csv content
        - filename format: yyyyMMddHHmmss.csv 
    
    2. Create application /home/watch_folder/watch_folder.pl and set it as a daemon.
        - Setup file path: /home/watch_folder/watch_folder.ini
        - Monitor path: /home/csv_folder/
        - APP path: /home/watch_folder/
        - Logs path: /home/logs/watch_folder/
            - logs name format: watch_folder-yyyy-MM-dd.log
        - Monitor the csv folder. If the csv folder is modified, the csv content will be automatically written to the DB.